291
00:16:41,465 --> 00:16:42,631
Je dérange pas ?

292
00:16:59,575 --> 00:17:00,611
Salut, Susan.

293
00:17:01,387 --> 00:17:02,480
Salut, toi.

294
00:17:08,237 --> 00:17:09,190
Tu fais quoi ?

295
00:17:09,716 --> 00:17:12,361
J'ai convaincu McCluskey de
prendre les enfants un moment,

296
00:17:12,398 --> 00:17:15,602
